    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4930971>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. (a–b) Habitat above Chilpancingo (17.63554°N, 99.52781°W, 1215 masl), Guerrero (habitat of Anolis microlepidotus); (c) Habitat at La Laguna, about 7 airline km E Omiltemi (17.55262°N, 99.62062°W, 1920 masl), Guerrero (habitat of A. omiltemanus); (d–f) Habitat near Omiltemi (17.55693°N, 99.68157°W, 1995 masl), Guerrero (habitat of A. liogaster, A. microlepidotus, and A. omiltemanus)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4930971/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4931269>
    dc:description "FIGURE 151. Anolis macrinii in life. (a) SMF 96208; (b) SMF 96387; (c) IBH 26577; (d) IBH 26583; (e) SMF 96209; (f) SMF 96648. (a–b,f) are adult males, (c, f) are adult females, (d) is a subadult female, (e) is a juvenile female." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4931269/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4931279>
    dc:description "FIGURE 156. Anolis macrinii: everted hemipenis of SMF 96387. (a) sulcate view; (b) asulcate view; (c) lateral view. Scale bar equals 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4931279/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4931283>
    dc:description "FIGURE 158. Dewlaps of Anolis unilobatus in life. (a) SMF 96471; (b) IBH 26570; (c) IBH 26609; (d) SMF 96278. (a–b) are males, (c–d) are females." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4931283/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

